{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"routermodule","title":"routerModule","subLink":null},{"id":"routermodule","title":"routerModule","subLink":[{"title":"authentication","id":"authentication","thirdLevelLink":[]},{"title":"authorization","id":"authorization","thirdLevelLink":[]},{"title":"middlewares","id":"middlewares","thirdLevelLink":[]},{"title":"urlEncryption","id":"urlencryption","thirdLevelLink":[]}]}],"title":"routerModule","description":"","validatorType":"validators","validationTypeTitle":"Validators","type":"simple","gitDocPath":"https://github.com/rxweb/rxweb.io/edit/master/docs/angular/routes/routerModule.md","category":"router","subCategory":"","linkTitle":"routerModule","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class='row page-section' id= 'routermodule'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>routerModule<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/router/routerModule/validators#routermodule'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The middlewares, authentication and authorization resolvers need to be configured globally in the <span class='highlighted'>@routerModule</span> along with the information of the encryption and multilingual components</p>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The configuration of middlewares, authentication, authorization are done in routerModule as below </p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"router-module-complete-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'authentication'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>authentication<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/router/routerModule/validators#authentication'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >In this parameter the Authentication resolver which resolves the necessary authentication requirements using the <span class='highlighted'>resolveAuth()</span> method.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"router-module-authentication-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'authorization'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>authorization<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/router/routerModule/validators#authorization'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To resolve the access to the particular user in respect to the module the Authorization resolver is used. </p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"router-module-authorize-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'middlewares'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>middlewares<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/router/routerModule/validators#middlewares'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >The application middleware used in the application used for the particular action to be called whenever any http request is called. For example </p>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >: GlobalMultilingualContentResolver, ComponentMultilingualContentResolver which are used to resolve global and component wise multilingual data.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"router-module-middlewares-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'urlencryption'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>urlEncryption<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/router/routerModule/validators#urlencryption'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >If the routing is to be done in encrypted form it is set to true.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"router-module-url-component\"></div> \r\n</div></div>\r\n"}